{"tid":2074943,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】巴西單日逾5萬4千宗確診　為全球之冠","createTime":"2020-06-22T13:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T14:48:16.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed79d0389792cde2e50c319e0a47294d0a4e4dc","tid":2074943,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/HYTGRFGH-1024x697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2FHYTGRFGH-1024x697.jpg&h=5cdf44de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【癲狗日報】武漢肺炎持續蔓延，其中巴西確診個案單日新增逾5萬4千宗，人數居全球之冠。<br />\n巴西衛生部表示，單日再新增54,771宗確診個案，再創單日新高，累計確診個案為106萬，近5萬人不治。<br />\n雖然疫情持續惡化，但當地並未有因疫情而鎖國，但各州都有各自採取不同的防疫措施。但由於疫情重創當地經濟，部份地區被迫解除封鎖措施，導致當地感染率仍然處於高水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/06/22/newsdesk/international/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e5%b7%b4%e8%a5%bf%e5%96%ae%e6%97%a5%e9%80%be5%e8%90%ac4%e5%8d%83%e5%ae%97%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba-%e7%82%ba%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e4%b9%8b%e5%86%a0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F22%2Fnewsdesk%2Finternational%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e5%2596%25ae%25e6%2597%25a5%25e9%2580%25be5%25e8%2590%25ac4%25e5%258d%2583%25e5%25ae%2597%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba-%25e7%2582%25ba%25e5%2585%25a8%25e7%2590%2583%25e4%25b9%258b%25e5%2586%25a0%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=b67e10e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/06/22/newsdesk/international/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e5%b7%b4%e8%a5%bf%e5%96%ae%e6%97%a5%e9%80%be5%e8%90%ac4%e5%8d%83%e5%ae%97%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba-%e7%82%ba%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e4%b9%8b%e5%86%a0/</a>"},{"pid":"bc715cd7f68b475b92e4ebdd80ba8d0910ae05eb","tid":2074943,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s